headline: ATO- One of My Favorite Utilities in a Booming Market
summary: Second-quarter earnings results and guidance updates are all in for CUI Portfolio recommendations. The big takeaway: The best-in-class are not just crushing it as businesses. They’re setting up for even better to come over the next few years. One of my favorite names is Atmos Energy Corp. (ATO), writes Roger Conrad, editor of Conrad’s Utility Investor.
